# Build-context exclusions for docker/Dockerfile (deliverable images) and the
# devcontainer Dockerfile. Shrinks context-upload time and avoids busting the
# cache on changes to files the image doesn't COPY. UPSTREAM_REVIEW.md M3.
#
# CAREFUL: docker/Dockerfile selectively COPYs *individual files* out of
# scripts/r_workflow/ and scripts/reference_scripts/, so we cannot exclude those
# directories wholesale. Only listed below are paths the build demonstrably
# does NOT touch.

# VCS / lint metadata — never COPYed.
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.gitmodules
.github
.pre-commit-config.yaml
.hadolint.yaml

# Docs / license / IDE — never COPYed (tests/ IS copied; not excluded).
docs
README.md
LICENSE
.vscode
.devcontainer
default.code-workspace

# Local-only state. Several are also gitignored — listed here too so a stale
# checkout can't ship them.
.devcontainer/fvs-bin
.claude-backup
data
outputs
logs
*.log
*.RData
*.db

# OS / editor noise.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
